{"tid":1437933,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒 由中國打響頭炮","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:02:25.000Z","uid":284104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"509f809c387859c0b388274603a28973e72fd79c","tid":1437933,"uid":284104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"國泰曾經示威既員工唔可以再執飛進入中國領空既航班<br />\n<br />\n如果海南空域都唔入得既話<br />\n佢地只係可以飛 <span style=\"color: blue;\">日韓台</span> <span style=\"color: violet;\">西岸</span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">東南亞</span>同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">澳洲</span><br />\n所有歐洲線中東線都基本上唔飛得<br />\n<br />\n但如果熟國泰既話會知道咁樣係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCwzBqh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCwzBqh.png&h=6842716d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}